metadata.name: The Lonely Kunoichi.
metadata.description:
ÅŒnin War | 1446
it was my first time down to earth.
And see Humans fight over their egos.
The Muromachi period is the witness 
where the ashes fly into the void.
576 years I lived, 
I wasted my time and
humans never change.

Awful.

Chiyo Katarina.
